Package: snow
Type: Package
Title: Snow Water Equivalent Analysis and Trend Detection
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Emma Gregory", "Emma_Gregory", email = "emma_gregory@gov.nt.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive R package for analyzing snow water equivalent (SWE) data from manual snow surveys and ERA5-Land reanalysis data. The package provides tools for trend analysis using Mann-Kendall tests, autocorrelation detection, spatial mapping, and comparison between observational and reanalysis datasets. Designed for analysis of snow survey data in the Northwest Territories, Canada.
